Create user and group :
Create new group -->sudo addgroup sre
add user in existing group -->sudo usermod -aG sre pslearner
creating user account --> sudo adduser --disabled-password --gecos "New SRE" jamie
sudo adduser -m username
Manage Passwords :
create user : sudo adduser --disabled-password --gecos "" terraform
sudo passwd terraform -->type password
su - terraform
To change the password -->passwd
userdel username--> to delete the user
sudo gpasswd -a jethalal devops-->to add the user in group
for multiple user --> -m
sudo groupdel groupname --->delete the group

